-- Roche Said to Sell Euro-Denominated Bonds Due June 2018
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n   a n d   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-03-14T08:57:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-14/roche-said-to-sell-euro-denominated-bonds-due-june-2018.html
Roche Holding Ltd. is selling bonds
in euros due June 2018, according to two people with knowledge
of the sale.  The bonds may be priced to yield about 30 basis points more
than the benchmark mid-swap rate, the people said.  BNP Paribas
SA,  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  and  UniCredit SpA (UCG)  are managing the deal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  